#: passwords.cpp:48
msgid "Echo characters as"
msgstr "Nyusela abasebenzi njenge"

#: passwords.cpp:49
msgid ""
"You can select the type of visual feedback given when you enter a password "
"in kdesu. Choose one of the following options:<p> <ul><li><em>1 star:</em> "
"each character you type is shown as an asterisk (*) symbol.</li> <li><em>3 "
"stars:</em> three asterisks are shown for each character you type.</li> "
"<li><em>no echo:</em>"
" there is no visual feedback at all, so nothing on your screen shows how "
"many characters are in your password.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"Ungakhetha udidi lengxelo ebonakalayo enikiweyo xa ufaka igama "
"eligqithisiweyo kwi kdesu. Khetha enye yezi nketho zilandelayo:<p> "
"<ul><li><em>1 star:</em> umsebenzi ngamnye owuchwethezayo uboniswa "
"njengophawu lukubhekisa(*).</li> <li><em>3 iinkwenkwezi:</em> iinkwenkwezi "
"ezintathu ziboniswa kumsebenzi ngamnye omchwethezayo.</li> <li><em>akukho "
"ngxolo:</em>  akukho ngxelo ibonakalayo, ngoko akukho nto kwikhusi lakho "
"ebonisa ukuba bangaphi abasebenzi kwigama lakho eligqithisiweyo.</li></ul>"

#: passwords.cpp:58
msgid "1 star"
msgstr "inkwenkwezi enye"

#: passwords.cpp:60
msgid "3 stars"
msgstr "iinkwenkwezi ezintathu"

#: passwords.cpp:62
msgid "no echo"
msgstr "akukho nyuko"

#: passwords.cpp:68
msgid "&Remember passwords"
msgstr "&Khumbula amagama agqithisiweyo"

#: passwords.cpp:69
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, kdesu will remember your passwords for the "
"specified amount of time. Until then, you won't have to enter your password "
"again. Keep in mind that this option is insecure and may enable others to "
"damage your system.<p> Please <em>do not</em> use this option if you are "
"working in an insecure environment, for example, on a workstation that is "
"located in a publicly accessible area.<p> This option does not affect "
"passwords explicitly set in other applications, for example, your email "
"account password in KMail."
msgstr ""
"Ukuba olu khetho lukhangelwe, kdesu izakukhumbula amagama wakho "
"agqithisiweyo e xesha elikhankanyiweyo. Kude kube ngoku, awunakungenisa "
"igama eligqithisiweyo kwakhona. Gcina engqondweni ukuba olu khetho "
"alukhuselekanga kwaye lungenza abanye bonakalise indlela yakho.<p> Nceda "
"<em>suku</em> sebenzisa olu khetho ukuba uya sebenza kwimeko bume "
"engakhuselekanga, umzekelo kwisitishi somsebenzi esikwi ariya enikezwe "
"kuwonke-wonke.<p> Olu khetho aluwachaphazeli amagama agqithisiweyo "
"acwangciswe kwezinye izicelo, umzekelo, ityala lakho le email yegama "
"eligqithisieyo kwi KMail."

#: passwords.cpp:80
msgid "&Timeout"
msgstr "&Ixesha lokuphuma"

#: passwords.cpp:85
msgid ""
"You can specify how long kdesu will remember your passwords. A short timeout "
"is more secure than a long timeout."
msgstr ""
"Ungagxininisa ukuba kukangakanani i kdesu izakukhumbula amagama "
"agqithisiweyo. Ixesha lokuphuma elifutshane lukhuseleke kakhulu kunexesha "
"elide lokuphuma."

#: passwords.cpp:92
msgid " minutes"
msgstr " imizuzu"

#: passwords.cpp:203
msgid ""
"<h1>Passwords</h1> This module gives you options for configuring the way in "
"which the \"kdesu\" program treats passwords. Kdesu will ask you for a "
"password when you try to carry out some privileged actions, such as changing "
"the date/time stored in your system clock, or adding new users on your "
"computer.<p> You can configure the type of visual feedback given when you "
"type a password, and whether kdesu should remember passwords for some time "
"after you have given them.<p> Note that these settings affect <em>only</em> "
"kdesu. This means that the behavior of passwords in KMail and other programs "
"cannot be configured here."
msgstr ""
"<h1>Amagama agqithisiweyo</h1> Lo mnqongo ukunika iinketho zokuqwalasela "
"indlela onoku \"kdesu\" udweliso lwenkqubo lujonga amagama agqithisiweyo. "
"Kdesu izakukubuza ngegama oligqithisileyo xa uzama ukukhupha izenzo zohlobo "
"oluthile, njengokutshintsha umhla/ixesha eligcinwe kwikloko yakho, okanye "
"udibanise abasebenzisi abatsha kwicomputer yakho.<p> Ungaqwalasela udidi "
"lwengxelo ebonakalayo oyinikiweyo xa uchwetheza igama eligqithisiweyo, kwaye "
"noba i kdesu ingakhumbula amagama agqithisiweyo ngexesha elithile emva "
"kokuba ubanikile.<p> Qaphela ukuba ezi zicwangciso zichaphazela "
"<em>kuphela</em> kdesu. Oku kuthetha ukuba ukuziphatha kwamagama "
"agqithisiweyo kwi KMail kunye nolunye udweliso lweenkqubo alunakuqwalaselwa "
"apha."
